#: src/Setup/Assets.php:164
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hostinger Reach is a Hostinger service that helps you create and send "
"branded email campaigns in minutes with smart AI tools. Hostinger Reach "
"WordPress Plugin allows you to connect and sync contacts from your favorite "
"WordPress plugins into Reach."
msgstr ""
"Hostinger Reach adalah layanan Hostinger yang membantu Anda membuat dan "
"mengirim kampanye email bermerek dalam hitungan menit dengan alat AI yang "
"cerdas. Plugin WordPress Hostinger Reach memungkinkan Anda untuk "
"menghubungkan dan menyinkronkan kontak dari plugin WordPress favorit Anda ke "
"dalam Reach."

#: src/Setup/Assets.php:158
msgid ""
"Hostinger Reach is an AI-powered email marketing tool for small businesses "
"and creators. It supports your entire email marketing journey—from building "
"contact lists to sending campaigns and tracking results."
msgstr ""
"Hostinger Reach adalah tool email marketing dengan AI untuk bisnis kecil dan "
"kreator. Reach mendukung seluruh proses email marketing Anda, mulai dari "
"membuat daftar kontak, mengirim campaign, hingga melacak performanya."

#: src/Setup/Assets.php:160
msgid ""
"Hostinger Reach is built for simplicity, speed, and results – no design or "
"marketing experience needed. Unlike most email tools, at the core of Reach "
"is its AI-powered template creator. Whether it is a product launch, special "
"offer, or newsletter update, it instantly crafts a professional, mobile-"
"friendly email. It not only writes the content for you; it also suggests the "
"best layout for your message and saves your style settings so you're never "
"starting from scratch.<br><br>Every template is customizable, so your emails "
"reflect your brand's look, feel, and voice. And because the templates are "
"built using proven best practices, they're optimized for readability, "
"accessibility, and reader engagement."
msgstr ""
"Hostinger Reach dirancang agar mudah digunakan, cepat, dan optimal meski "
"tanpa pengalaman desain atau marketing. Berbeda dari tool email lainnya, "
"Reach menyediakan template berteknologi AI. Baik untuk peluncuran produk, "
"penawaran spesial, atau newsletter, AI langsung membuat email yang "
"profesional dan mobile-friendly. Tidak hanya menulis konten untuk Anda, "
"tetapi juga menyarankan layout terbaik dan menyimpan pengaturan style "
"sehingga tidak perlu mulai dari nol.<br><br>Setiap template bisa "
"dikustomisasi, jadi email Anda pasti sesuai dengan gaya dan karakter dari "
"brand Anda. Selain itu, karena template dibuat sesuai strategi terbaik yang "
"terbukti efektif, semuanya optimal untuk memudahkan audiens membaca, "
"mengakses, dan berinteraksi."

